{"tid":2141842,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"政府送大禮系列","createTime":"2020-08-06T04:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T13:26:22.000Z","uid":19552,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e9531648a751f5861857fb75604d4f629cc53f48","tid":2141842,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:17:08.000Z","msg":"公屋客刀仔鋸大樹 3000元首期入市 賣樓即賺380萬<br />\n<br />\n房委會計劃年底重推「租置公屋」餘貨，首批至少441伙，以市值一五折至一八折發售，即時成為市場焦點，因為分分鐘成為綠表家庭置富途徑。土地註冊資料顯示，鴨脷洲利東邨東平樓（第6座）中層4室，實用面積490平方呎，於7月底綠表市場以440萬元（未補地價）成交，呎價8,980元，成為屋苑第二貴價單位。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於17年3月以60.3萬元購入，當時只支付3000元首期，持貨3年，帳面獲利約379.7萬元，期內升值逾6倍，可算是一個經典刀仔鋸大樹的成功典範。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，全港有39條租置屋邨，共有約18.4萬個單位，樓齡介乎25至38年，最新仍有4.03萬伙未售，不排除有更多成功例子出現。"},{"pid":"8b6dec4677cd427ff8a704363bb0263cee960cf6","tid":2141842,"uid":124,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"賣左買唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29d3e0ac3eca76f14aba340b6e9879d7222a086","tid":2141842,"uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"8b6dec4677cd427ff8a704363bb0263cee960cf6","tid":2141842,"uid":124,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"賣左買唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"380萬首期借多兩三球有私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb0193cff6d511eb5164e43e3a3f51bcace69ae","tid":2141842,"uid":125261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"0.5% 首期？"},{"pid":"eafa35e087ae1c3ff500d0e72a35e4c99fda56ad","tid":2141842,"uid":199482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:31:53.000Z","msg":"香港點會有窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係無轉售限制既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde8eaef8a00302e05980e9df9fa4c55fe5af753","tid":2141842,"uid":1